    <string name="message_star_benefits">• Help others discover this app\n• Support free and open-source software\n• Motivate us to add more features\n• Join our growing community</string>
    <string name="message_about_intro">VigiLens (Background Video Recorder) is a professional-grade video recording application designed for discrete documentation needs. We prioritize privacy, efficiency, and user experience in every aspect of our design.</string>
    <string name="message_about_privacy">With a focus on reliability, VigiLens operates completely offline and stores all recordings locally on your device. We\'ve optimized the app for high-quality HD recording while maintaining efficient battery usage and system resource management.</string>
    <string name="message_about_features">VigiLens offers essential features for professional and academic use, including background recording capability, secure storage implementation, and customizable quick-access controls. The app maintains full functionality even with the screen off to ensure discrete operation.</string>
    <string name="message_about_opensource">As an open-source project, VigiLens maintains transparency while continuously improving through community contributions. Our commitment remains focused on providing a robust, secure, and privacy-respecting recording solution.</string>
    <string name="message_about_team">Developed and maintained by the VigiLens Development Team</string>
    <string name="message_thank_you">We appreciate you taking the time to provide feedback. Your input helps us improve the app for everyone.</string>


